item.title: What I Did On My Holidays
item.description: And now, a post for my long-neglected, less technical readers. I took a week off in July to try and avoid that Oh My God I Missed Summer Again feeling. Granted, it’s easy to get that in the UK even if you’re not stuck in an office the entire time. Really this is just an excuse to post some photos on the blog. Monday Hopped on the bike and explored from Kensington to Westminster.
